This can be used to make redirect with return URL, like this:

    SESSION_LOGIN_URL = lambda request: '/login?return='+request.path
    
    @app.route('/secure')
    def secure(request):
       return request.user

    @app.route('/login')
    def login(request):
        # ...do a login...
        return HTTPFound(request.GET.get('return', '/'))

